# CHANGELOG

# Changes in version 1.1.0

* Added strict bool check methods `isTrue` / `isFalse` and `isTrueOrNull` / `isFalseOrtNull`
* Added `when` method to conditionally skip a number of following check methods
* Added a `when...` method for each check method to make the check result a condition
* Changed modifier of `getValue` from `protected` to `public` to give direct access to values from a data provider

See [README](./README.md) for a full method list and details.